{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "knowledge-base-collection",
    "name": "MeepleAI - Knowledge Base",
    "description": "KnowledgeBase bounded context endpoints for MeepleAI API.\n\n**Includes**:\n- Hybrid RAG search (vector + keyword RRF fusion)\n- Q&A agent with streaming support\n- Explain agent (detailed topic explanations)\n- Setup guide agent\n- Chess agent (move suggestions, position analysis)\n- Agent feedback collection\n\n**Architecture**: CQRS/MediatR with KnowledgeBase bounded context\n**RAG Pipeline**: Hybrid Search (70% vector + 30% keyword) → Multi-model LLM → 5-layer validation\n\n**Base URL**: `{{base_url}}/api/v1`\n\n**Version**: 1.0.0\n**Last Updated**: 2025-11-20",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "noauth"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Search & Retrieval",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Hybrid Search (Vector + Keyword)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function() {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has success flag', function() {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(response.success).to.be.true;",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has results array', function() {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(response.results).to.be.an('array');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Search mode is hybrid', function() {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(response.searchMode).to.equal('hybrid');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Results have relevance scores', function() {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (response.results.length > 0) {",
                  "        pm.expect(response.results[0]).to.have.property('relevanceScore');",
                  "        pm.expect(response.results[0].relevanceScore).to.be.a('number');",
                  "    }",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"gameId\": \"{{game_id}}\",\n  \"query\": \"How do you win?\",\n  \"topK\": 5,\n  \"minScore\": 0.7,\n  \"searchMode\": \"hybrid\",\n  \"language\": \"en\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/knowledge-base/search",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "knowledge-base", "search"]
            },
            "description": "Test hybrid search (vector + keyword fusion via RRF).\n\n**Query**: SearchQuery\n**Handler**: SearchQueryHandler\n**Context**: KnowledgeBase\n**Services**: VectorSearchDomainService + RrfFusionDomainService\n**Algorithm**: RRF (Reciprocal Rank Fusion) with 70/30 weighting"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Vector Only Search",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
